messageBody:

> >>
> >> ??
> >>
> >> collectionB.containsAll(collectionA) == true
> >
> > How is that true? collectionB does not contain "x".

Oops, guess I missed the whole point of that one. I think I need paired
emailing also;)

Jason Rogers
